    /// bounded by a bordered box that stretches from the top to the bottom of
    /// the screen's safe area. Button 1 has focus, indicated by its bright
    /// color and larger size than other buttons. At the bottom right, three
    /// buttons labeled A, B, and C are in another box that stretches from top
    /// to bottom. No button is directly across from any other button
    /// horizontally.](View-focusSection-tvOS)
