    /// declare itself as a focus section, it is impossible to direct focus
    /// back to the left from buttons "A" - "C". None of those buttons has
    /// a focusable view --- in this case either a button or a ``VStack`` with
    /// the `focusSection()` modifier --- directly to its left.
